AVERMEDIA INFO said unconsolidated sales
in April fell 24.26% to NT$126,827,000 from NT$167,445,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  4/2012           4/2011
Sales            126,827          167,445    
YOY%             -24.26%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            425,170          581,713    
YOY%             -26.91% 
=================================================================
 